        <Rows>
          <Row>
            <Col id="title01">학생 여러분, 안녕하세요.</Col>
            <Col id="title02">여러분의 솔직한 응답이 행복하고 안전한 학교를 만듭니다.</Col>
            <Col id="title03">2024년 2학기부터 지금까지 본인이 직접 경험한 학교폭력에 대해 응답해주세요.</Col>
            <Col id="title04">※ 2024년 2학기 이후 발생한 학교폭력이라면 해결 중에 있거나 이미 해결된 일이라도 응답해주세요.</Col>
            <Col id="title05_1">* 학교폭력이란? </Col>
            <Col id="title05_2">학교 안과 밖에서 학생에게 피해를 주는 행동</Col>
            <Col id="button01">참여하기</Col>
            <Col id="title11">전국 시‧도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="title09">음성 재생을 원하시는 경우, &lt;img src='/images/sts/svs_new/icon_sound_on.png' class='img_vol'&gt;버튼을 눌러 주시기 바랍니다.</Col>
            <Col id="title08_2">감사합니다.</Col>
            <Col id="title08_1">응답 내용은 통계법 제 33조에 의해 비밀이 지켜지므로 안심하고 응답해 주시기 바랍니다.</Col>
            <Col id="title07">사소한 괴롭힘이나 장난도 학교폭력이 될 수 있습니다.</Col>
            <Col id="title06_8">집단 따돌림 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_7">스토킹 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_6">사이버 폭력 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_5">성폭력 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_4">신체폭력 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_3">금품갈취 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_2">강요 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_1">언어폭력 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_1_1">심한 욕설, 놀림, 협박(겁주는 말)을 함</Col>
            <Col id="title06_2_1">친구나 선·후배가 하기 싫은 일을 강제로 시킴</Col>
            <Col id="title06_3_1">내가 가지고 있는 돈이나 물건을 빼앗음</Col>
            <Col id="title06_4_1">친구나 선·후배에게 맞거나 어떤 곳에 갇힘</Col>
            <Col id="title06_5_1">성희롱, 성추행, 성폭행 등의 괴롭힘</Col>
            <Col id="title06_6_1">사이버 공간(예: 인터넷, 스마트폰 등)에서 괴롭힘</Col>
            <Col id="title06_7_1">상대방(해당 학생)이 싫다고 하는데도 계속 따라다니며 괴롭힘</Col>
            <Col id="title06_8_1">친구나 선·후배 여러 명이 계속 따돌림</Col>
            <Col id="button02">취소</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmB10">서울특별시교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmC10">부산광역시교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmD10">대구광역시교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmE10">인천광역시교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmF10">광주광역시교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmG10">대전광역시교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmH10">울산광역시교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmI10">세종특별자치시교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmJ10">경기도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmK10">강원특별자치도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmM10">충청북도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmN10">충청남도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmP10">전북특별자치도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmR10">경상북도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmS10">경상남도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmT10">제주특별자치도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmQ10">전라남도교육감</Col>
            <Col id="title10">2025. 4.</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col id="title01">Hello students.</Col>
            <Col id="title02">Your honest responses to this survey will help make our school a safer and happier place.</Col>
            <Col id="title03">Please respond about any school violence you have personally experienced from the second semester of 2024 until now.</Col>
            <Col id="title04">※ If you have experienced any school violence that occurred after the second semester of 2024, please respond even if it is in the process of being resolved or has already been resolved.</Col>
            <Col id="title05_1">* What is school violence? </Col>
            <Col id="title05_2">Actions that harm students, both inside and outside of school</Col>
            <Col id="button01">Participate</Col>
            <Col id="title11">City and provincial superintendent of education</Col>
            <Col id="title09">Click on &lt;img src='/images/sts/svs_new/icon_sound_on.png' class='img_vol'&gt;the icon to listen to the recording.</Col>
            <Col id="title08_2">Thank you.</Col>
            <Col id="title08_1">Your responses will be kept strictly confidential under Article 33 of the Statistics Act, so please feel free to answer truthfully.</Col>
            <Col id="title07">Minor teasing or pranks can also be considered school violence.</Col>
            <Col id="title06_8">Group bullying :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_7">Stalking :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_6">Cyberbullying :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_5">Sexual violence :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_4">Physical violence :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_3">Extortion :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_2">Coercion :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_1">Verbal abuse :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_1_1">Using severe curse words, teasing, and making threats/intimidating remarks</Col>
            <Col id="title06_2_1">Friends or peers forcing someone to do something they do not want to do</Col>
            <Col id="title06_3_1">Stealing my money or belongings</Col>
            <Col id="title06_4_1">Hitting or confining someone to a specific place by friends or peers</Col>
            <Col id="title06_5_1">Sexual harassment, molestation, sexual assault, or any form of sexual abuse</Col>
            <Col id="title06_6_1">Harassment that occurs in cyberspace (e.g. internet, smartphone, etc.)</Col>
            <Col id="title06_7_1">Continuing to follow and harass someone even after they have expressed their discomfort</Col>
            <Col id="title06_8_1">Continuous bullying by friends or peers</Col>
            <Col id="button02">cancel</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmB10">Superintendent of Seoul Metropolitan Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmC10">Superintendent of Busan Metropolitan City Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmD10">Superintendent of Daegu Metropolitan City Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmE10">Superintendent of Incheon Metropolitan City Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmF10">Superintendent of Gwangju Metropolitan City Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmG10">Superintendent of Daejeon Metropolitan City Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmH10">Superintendent of Ulsan Metropolitan City Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmI10">Superintendent of Sejong Metropolitan City Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmJ10">Superintendent of Gyeonggi-do Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmK10">Superintendent of Gangwon-do State Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmM10">Superintendent of Chungcheongbuk-do Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmN10">Superintendent of Chungcheongnam-do Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmP10">Superintendent of Jeonbuk State Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmR10">Superintendent of Gyeongsangbuk-do Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmS10">Superintendent of Gyeongsangnam-do Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmT10">Superintendent of Jeju Special Self-Governing Provincial Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmQ10">Superintendent of Jeollanam-do Office of Education</Col>
            <Col id="title10">April 2025</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col id="title01">各位同学，大家好！</Col>
            <Col id="title02">请大家如实回答以下内容，共同建立幸福安全的校园。</Col>
            <Col id="title03">请就2024年第二学期至今本人亲身经历的校园暴力进行作答。</Col>
            <Col id="title04">※ 回答范围包括2024年第二学期以后发生的正在解决或已经解决的全部校园暴力事件。</Col>
            <Col id="title05_1">* 什么是校园暴力？ </Col>
            <Col id="title05_2">校内外对学生造成伤害的行为</Col>
            <Col id="button01">参与</Col>
            <Col id="title11">全韩国市、道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="title09">若想播放语音，请点击&lt;img src='/images/sts/svs_new/icon_sound_on.png' class='img_vol'&gt;按钮。</Col>
            <Col id="title08_2">谢谢。</Col>
            <Col id="title08_1">所有回答依据《统计法》第33条严格保密，请放心作答。</Col>
            <Col id="title07">再小的霸凌或玩笑也可能成为校园暴力。</Col>
            <Col id="title06_8">集体孤立 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_7">跟踪骚扰 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_6">网络暴力 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_5">性暴力 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_4">身体暴力 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_3">勒索钱财 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_2">强迫 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_1">语言暴力 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_1_1">严重的辱骂、嘲弄、威胁（恐吓）</Col>
            <Col id="title06_2_1">被同年级、高年级或低年级同学强行指使做不想做的事情</Col>
            <Col id="title06_3_1">抢夺我的钱财或物品</Col>
            <Col id="title06_4_1">被同年级、高年级或低年级同学殴打或关在某个地方</Col>
            <Col id="title06_5_1">性骚扰、猥亵、性暴力等折磨</Col>
            <Col id="title06_6_1">在网络空间（例：互联网、智能手机等）霸凌</Col>
            <Col id="title06_7_1">对方（相应同学）明确表示不喜欢但依然跟在身边进行骚扰</Col>
            <Col id="title06_8_1">持续被多名同年级、高年级或低年级同学孤立</Col>
            <Col id="button02">取消</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmB10">首尔特别市教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmC10">釜山广域市教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmD10">大邱广域市教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmE10">仁川广域市教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmF10">光州广域市教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmG10">大田广域市教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmH10">蔚山广域市教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmI10">世宗特别自治市教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmJ10">京畿道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmK10">江原特别自治道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmM10">忠清北道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmN10">忠清南道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmP10">全北特别自治道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmR10">庆尚北道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmS10">庆尚南道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmT10">济州特别自治道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="cddcNmQ10">全罗南道教育监</Col>
            <Col id="title10">2025年4月</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col id="title01">皆さん、こんにちは。</Col>
            <Col id="title02">皆さんの率直な回答が幸せで安全な学校をつくります。</Col>
            <Col id="title03">2024年2学期から 現在まで、あなた自身が直接経験した校内暴力について回答してください。</Col>
            <Col id="title04">※ 2024年2学期以降に 発生した校内暴力であれば、解決しつつあったり、すでに解決済みだとしても回答してください。</Col>
            <Col id="title05_1">* 校内暴力とは？ </Col>
            <Col id="title05_2">学校の中あるいは外で、他の子に被害を及ぼす行動</Col>
            <Col id="button01">参加する</Col>
            <Col id="title11">全国市・道教育監</Col>
            <Col id="title09">音声を再生したい場合、&lt;img src='/images/sts/svs_new/icon_sound_on.png' class='img_vol'&gt;ボタンを押してください。</Col>
            <Col id="title08_2">ありがとうございます。</Col>
            <Col id="title08_1">回答内容は、統計法第33条に基づき秘密が保持されますので、安心して自由に回答してください。</Col>
            <Col id="title07">ささいな嫌がらせやいたずらも校内暴力になることがあります。</Col>
            <Col id="title06_8">仲間外れ :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_7">ストーキング :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_6">サイバー暴力 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_5">性暴力 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_4">身体的な暴力 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_3">金品のゆすり :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_2">強要 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_1">言葉の暴力 :</Col>
            <Col id="title06_1_1">酷い悪口、からかう言葉、脅迫(恐怖を与える言葉)を言う。</Col>
            <Col id="title06_2_1">友達や先輩・後輩が、やりたくないことを無理やりさせる。</Col>
            <Col id="title06_3_1">持っていたお金や物などを奪う。</Col>
            <Col id="title06_4_1">友達や先輩・後輩に叩かれたり、ある場所に閉じ込められる。</Col>
            <Col id="title06_5_1">セクハラ、性的嫌がらせ、性的暴行などをする。</Col>
            <Col id="title06_6_1">サイバー空間(例：インターネット、スマートフォンなど)で嫌がらせをする。</Col>
            <Col id="title06_7_1">相手が嫌だと言っているのに、つきまといを繰り返して苦しめる。</Col>
            <Col id="title06_8_1">複数の友達や先輩・後輩が仲間外れにする</Col>
